   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The general station description (GSD) file extension used is developed
by PROFIBUS &amp; PROFINET International. The GSD file defines how
devices communicates on a Profibus-DP bus.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">When using the LUFP7 gateway on a Profibus-DP bus the primary device
must use the GSD file: <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">tele071f-gsd-file-for-profibus-v3.gsd</codeph>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">For additional information about the LUFP7 gateway and download
of the GSD file for implementation see <xref href="https://www.anybus.com/lufp"
               scope="external"
               class="- topic/xref "
               format="html">https://www.anybus.com/lufp</xref>.</p>
